GTG for now. Good night, everyone.

::Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike nods. "Allrighty, here ya go," he says, walking over to a 
console and pressing a few buttons. A brown bot appears in the middle of the 
room, instantly taking out a sword and jumping at Skulletron.

(If you could finish off this bot by tomorrow, Dcoburn, we could get back to 
sparring then. You can controll this hologram.)
